# vim: syn=perl

=head1 NAME

UNTRIM_JSA_TILES - Restore JSA tiles to full size

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This recipe takes JSA-tiled data files and untrims them so that they each
cover the whole area of the corresponding JSA tiles.

